data.title: Equatorial Guinea Money supply, billion currency units, July, 2023 - data, chart
data.meta_description: Money supply, billion currency units in  Equatorial Guinea, July, 2023 The most recent value is 1331.81 billion CFA Franc as of July 2023, an increase compared to the previous value of 1256.15 billion CFA Franc. Historically, the average for Equatorial Guinea from December 2017 to July 2023 is 1095.2 billion CFA Franc. The minimum of 940.3 billion CFA Franc was recorded in February 2021, while the maximum of 1331.81 billion CFA Franc was reached in July 2023. | TheGlobalEconomy.com
